---
// Mi Experiencia
---

<section class="experiencia-section">
  <h2 class="experiencia-title">MI EXPERIENCIA REAL</h2>
  <p class="experiencia-desc">No tengo títulos rimbombantes, pero tengo experiencia real: he pasado por mil historias, oficios y entornos distintos. De todos me llevé algo: adaptarme rápido, encontrar soluciones y sacar las cosas adelante.</p>
  <div class="experiencia-section-inner" style="max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="experiencia-grid">
      <div class="exp-card exp-card-left exp-card-yellow">
        <div class="exp-card-content improved">
          <h2 class="exp-card-yellow-title">De dónde sale todo esto</h2>
          <p class="exp-card-desc">
            No tengo un MBA, pero sí lo que llamo el máster del universo.<br /><br />
            He hecho de todo: camarera, dependienta, limpiadora de discotecas, auxiliar de veterinaria, diseñadora de bolsos, emprendedora, y hasta trabajé en un convento (sin ser monja).<br /><br />
            He pasado por mil oficios y entornos, y de cada uno me llevé algo: adaptarme rápido, resolver problemas y sacar adelante lo que me propongo.<br /><br />
            No tengo títulos rimbombantes, pero sí experiencia real.<br />
          </p>
          <button class="exp-btn exp-btn-yellow">Descargar mi CV</button>
        </div>
      </div>
  <div class="exp-experience-center-white exp-card">
        <ul class="exp-experience-list">
          <li>
            <span class="exp-years">2023 – Present</span><br />
            <span class="exp-role">ART DIRECTOR</span><br />
            <span class="exp-company">ALEPLABS</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="exp-years">2017 – 2020</span><br />
            <span class="exp-role">Graphic Designer</span><br />
            <span class="exp-company">CLIPOINT</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="exp-card-photo-vertical">
          <img src="/images/ana2corta.png" alt="Portrait Experience Photo" />
        </div>
        <ul class="exp-experience-list">
          <li>
            <span class="exp-years">2020 – 2023</span><br />
            <span class="exp-role">UI/UX Designer</span><br />
            <span class="exp-company">BAHEUS</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="exp-years">2015 – 2017</span><br />
            <span class="exp-role">Logo Designer</span><br />
            <span class="exp-company">DASTUDIO</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@import '../styles/palette.css';
.experiencia-section {
  background: var(--color-almost-white);
  padding: 4em 2vw 4em 2vw;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.experiencia-title {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 2em;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  color: var(--color-dark);
}
.experiencia-desc {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--color-info);
  margin-bottom: 2.5em;
  font-size: 1.25em;
}
.experiencia-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2em;
  align-items: stretch;
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.exp-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.08);
  padding: 1.5em;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%;
  min-width: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  min-height: 540px;
  height: 100%;
}
  .exp-card-left {
    grid-column: 1 / 2;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: stretch;
    text-align: left;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    padding: 2.5em 2em 2em 2em;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 32px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.10);
  }

.exp-experience-center-white {
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: #fff;
}

.exp-card-photo-top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  width: 100%;
}
.exp-card-photo-top img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 180px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.12);
  border: 4px solid #fff;
}
.exp-card-content.improved {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.5em;
  text-align: left;
  font-size : 1.25em;
}
.exp-card-name {
  font-size: 1.3em;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-dark);
  margin: 0.2em 0 0 0;
}
.exp-card-role {
  font-size: 1.25em;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
}
.exp-card-desc {
  color: var(--color-dark);
  font-size: 1.25em;
  margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  text-align: left;
}
.exp-card-left img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 1em;
}
.exp-card-content p {
  color: var(--color-dark);
  margin-bottom: 1.2em;
}
.exp-btn {
  background: var(--color-dark);
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 0.7em 1.5em;
  font-size: 1.25em;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.08);
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.exp-btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary);
}
.exp-experience-center-white {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px 1fr;
  gap: 2em;
  text-align: right;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.08);
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: 2em;
  width: 100%;
  min-width: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  min-height: 540px;
  color: #fff;
}
.exp-card-photo-vertical {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  filter: zoom(1.2);
}
.exp-card-photo-vertical img {
  width: 280px;
  height: 480px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.08);
  transform: rotate(-4deg);
}
.exp-job {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px 0 rgba(17,138,178,0.08);
  padding: 1.2em 1.5em;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.exp-experience-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2em;
  min-width: 160px;
}
.exp-experience-list li {
  background: none;
  box-shadow: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  padding: 0;
  color: var(--color-dark);
  font-size: 1.25em;
  text-align: right;
}
.exp-experience-list:last-child li {
  text-align: left;
}
.exp-years {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 0.95em;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.exp-role {
  color: var(--color-dark);
  font-size: 1.25em;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin: 0.2em 0 0.1em 0;
}
.exp-company {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-size: 1.25em;
  font-weight: 600;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .experiencia-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
    gap: 2em;
  }
  .exp-card, .exp-card-photo, .exp-timeline {
    grid-column: auto;
  }
  .exp-experience-center-white {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1em;
    padding: 1em 0.5em;
  }
  .exp-card-photo-vertical img {
    width: 90vw;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 320px;
    min-width: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .experiencia-section {
    padding: 2em 1vw;
  }
  .experiencia-title {
    font-size: 1.3em;
  }
  .experiencia-desc {
    font-size: 1em;
  }
  .exp-card {
    padding: 1em 0.5em;
    min-height: 320px;
  }
}
</style>
